> I get quite a few engines brought to me with just one paper gasket and the
> metal gasket. I always lay down Permatex 3-H, a paper gasket, more 3-H,
the
> metal baffle, more 3-H, the other paper gasket, and more 3-H. That is one
of
> the places I never leak!
